                        <h2>Welcome to our organization</h2>
                        <div style=" min-height: 400px; padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 22px; padding-top: 5px;">
                            <p>Do you have the spiritual gift of giving? If so, we want to expand your giving horizons. We 
                            currently have four categories: The Poor, The Sick, Ministries and Microbusinesses, but we plan 
                            to offer more. Suggest a new one to us!</p>
                            <p>TargetedHelp.org is a new concept that is long overdue - bringing giving into the Information Age. 
                            By giving directly to those in need, we cut the cost of giving to a minimum and empower charitable 
                            organizations with a &quot;presence on the ground&quot; to focus on their more vital role of collecting
                            information. </p>
                            <p>&nbsp;</p>
